<p>Technology providers are reaping the rewards of these remote processes, with video conferencing app Zoom posting a 355% increase in revenue for May through to July 2020.</p>

<p>And while it may be tempting to rely wholly on tech tools, it&rsquo;s incumbent on HR to continue to uphold best practices during the crisis.</p>

